5759</a>)<br />\n每日幾秒，洗版派嬲＋推post<br />\n堅持洗版直到勝利<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">洗版唔會益咗廣告商</span>，我哋睇實際效果：洗版派嬲確實令廣告減少<br />\n我唔想做標題黨先呃到你入嚟..."},{"pid":"dab23e4454e5e7aef1f2b238a798b96e4b76030f","tid":1867292,"uid":267969,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span>  <br />\n消費前諗清楚：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=3a14eb7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n週街貼文宣圖：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Mc2yKv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Mc2yKv&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b5a964c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Mc2yKv</a><br />\n－－－－－－－  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong><br />\nFacebook:  <a href=\"http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=2387a618\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=699fdcce\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=209a8609\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"05861b31af5259c0a0ad57b8bd754ae254042311","tid":1867292,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkg